#: app/templates/about.html:10
msgid "About Grylli"
msgstr "Sobre Grylli"

#: app/templates/about.html:13
msgid ""
"Grylli is a secure, self-hosted message delivery platform that automatically"
" sends pre-configured messages if a user fails to check in within a defined "
"time period."
msgstr ""
"Grylli é unha plataforma de entrega de mensaxes segura e autoaloxada que "
"envía mensaxes preconfiguradas automaticamente se un usuario non fai check-"
"in dentro dun prazo definido."

#: app/templates/about.html:14
msgid ""
"It supports multiple users, customizable schedules, and recurring reminders."
msgstr "Admite varios usuarios e horarios personalizables."

#: app/templates/about.html:15
msgid ""
"Messages and reminders can be delivered via email, webhooks, or over 100 "
"third-party services through Apprise."
msgstr ""
"As mensaxes pódense entregar por correo electrónico, webhooks ou a través de"
" máis de 80 servizos de terceiros mediante Apprise."

#: app/templates/about.html:16
msgid ""
"Users can configure their own SMTP servers to ensure emails and reminders "
"appear to come directly from them — not from the system administrator."
msgstr ""
"Os usuarios poden configurar os seus propios servidores SMTP para asegurarse"
" de que as mensaxes semellen vir directamente deles — non do administrador "
"do sistema."

#: app/templates/about.html:17
msgid ""
"Sensitive data is encrypted at rest, and all operations are secured with "
"strong authentication and audit-friendly logging."
msgstr ""
"Os datos sensibles son cifrados en repouso e todas as operacións de mensaxes"
" están protexidas con unha forte autenticación e rexistros amigables coa "
"auditoría."

#: app/templates/about.html:18
msgid ""
"Built with a modern, reactive technology stack, Grylli is optimized for "
"responsiveness and works seamlessly across desktop and mobile devices."
msgstr ""
"Construído cunha pila tecnolóxica moderna e reactiva, Grylli está optimizado"
" para a reactividade e funciona sen problemas tanto en dispositivos de "
"escritorio como móbiles."

#: app/templates/about.html:23
msgid "Version:"
msgstr "Versión:"

#: app/templates/about.html:26
msgid "Repository:"
msgstr "Repositorio:"

#: app/templates/about.html:30
msgid "GitHub - samcro1967/grylli"
msgstr "GitHub - samcro1967/grylli"

